== Note Tag ==
{{{
{{{
#!html
<div style="background-color:#8e9f00; color:white; background-image:url('/spacewalk/attachment/wiki/Conventions/note.png?format=raw'); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:7em;background-position:1em;" >
   <h2>Note</h2>
   <div style="padding-bottom:0.5em;" >
       A note is a tip or shortcut or alternative approach to the task at hand. Ignoring a note should have no negative consequences, but you might miss out on a trick that makes your life easier.
   </div>
</div>
}}}
}}}

