== Warning Tag ==
{{{
{{{
#!html
<div style="background-color:#9e292b; color:white; background-image:url('/spacewalk/attachment/wiki/Conventions/warning.png?format=raw'); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:7em;background-position:1em;" >
   <h2>Warning</h2>
   <div style="padding-bottom:0.5em;" >
      A Warning should not be ignored. Ignoring warnings will most likely cause data loss.
   </div>
</div>
}}}
}}}

